title: For Sale:  Browning A-5 A5 12ga Magnum, 1959 BOXED w/papers
postcontent: Super-early Magnum 12ga in serialized box with original paperwork. This is the only Auto-5 from this period that I have been able to own that retained the box, and that in fantastic shape. The gun has been hunted with, but not abused and remains in very high condition. The only paperwork not present is the instruction card for installation of the magazine plug, though the envelope is there. Magnums from the 1958-60 period are uncommon in high condition as most were hunted hard and saw extensive use in duck blinds and so-on. For an advanced Browning collection and an owner who still enjoys shooting their investments, this represents an extremely rare package
